{"id":269,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":269,"title":"Revelation 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","He who overcomes will retain his name in the book of life, reach godhood, and be with Jesus as He is with the Father."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1","order":"03.29.003.27301"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"And"],"unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"angel"],"of the church in Sardis write; These things saith he that hath the seven",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"Spirits"],"of God, and the seven",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"stars"],"; I",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"know"],"thy works, that thou hast a name that thou livest, and art",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_1f"},"dead"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.2","order":"03.29.003.27302"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Be"],"watchful, and strengthen the things which remain, that are ready to die: for I have not found thy works perfect before God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.3","order":"03.29.003.27303"},["b","3"],"Remember therefore how thou hast received and heard, and hold fast, and repent. If therefore thou shalt not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"watch"],", I will come on thee as a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"thief"],", and thou shalt not know what hour I will come upon thee."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4","order":"03.29.003.27304"},["b","4"],"Thou hast a few names even in Sardis which have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"defiled"],"their garments; and they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"walk"],"with me in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"white"],": for they are",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"worthy"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5","order":"03.29.003.27305"},["b","5"],"He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"overcometh"],", the same shall be clothed in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"white"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"raiment"],"; and I will not",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"blot out"],"his name out of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_5e"},"book of life"],", but I will",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_5f"},"confess"],"his name before my Father, and before his angels."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.6","order":"03.29.003.27306"},["b","6"],"He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.7","order":"03.29.003.27307"},["b","7"],"And to the angel of the church in Philadelphia write; These things saith he that is holy, he that is true, he that hath the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"key"],"of David, he that openeth, and no man shutteth; and shutteth, and no man openeth;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.8","order":"03.29.003.27308"},["b","8"],"I know thy works: behold, I have set before thee an open door, and no man can shut it: for thou hast a little strength, and hast kept my word, and hast not denied my name."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.9","order":"03.29.003.27309"},["b","9"],"Behold, I will make them of the synagogue of Satan, which say they are Jews, and are not, but do lie; behold, I will make them to come and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"worship"],"before thy feet, and to know that I have loved thee."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.10","order":"03.29.003.27310"},["b","10"],"Because thou hast kept the word of my patience, I also will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"keep"],"thee from the hour of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"temptation"],", which shall come upon all the world, to try them that dwell upon the earth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.11","order":"03.29.003.27311"},["b","11"],"Behold, I come",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"quickly"],": hold that fast which thou hast, that no man take thy crown."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.12","order":"03.29.003.27312"},["b","12"],"Him that overcometh will I make a pillar in the temple of my God, and he shall go no more out: and I will write upon him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"name"],"of my God, and the name of the city of my God,",["i","which is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"new Jerusalem"],", which cometh down out of heaven from my God: and",["i","I will write upon him"],"my new name."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.13","order":"03.29.003.27313"},["b","13"],"He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.14","order":"03.29.003.27314"},["b","14"],"And unto the angel of the church of the Laodiceans write; These things saith the Amen, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"faithful"],"and true witness, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"beginning"],"of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"creation"],"of God;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.15","order":"03.29.003.27315"},["b","15"],"I know thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"works"],", that thou art neither cold nor hot: I would thou wert cold or hot."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.16","order":"03.29.003.27316"},["b","16"],"So then because thou art",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"lukewarm"],", and neither cold nor hot, I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"spue"],"thee out of my mouth."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.17","order":"03.29.003.27317"},["b","17"],"Because thou sayest, I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"rich"],", and increased with goods, and have need of nothing; and knowest not that thou art wretched, and miserable, and poor, and blind, and naked:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.18","order":"03.29.003.27318"},["b","18"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"counsel"],"thee to buy of me",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"gold"],"tried in the fire, that thou mayest be rich; and white raiment, that thou mayest be clothed, and",["i","that"],"the shame of thy nakedness do not appear; and anoint thine eyes with eyesalve, that thou mayest see."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.19","order":"03.29.003.27319"},["b","19"],"As many as I love, I rebuke and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"chasten"],": be zealous therefore, and repent."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.20","order":"03.29.003.27320"},["b","20"],"Behold, I stand at the door, and knock: if any man hear my voice, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"open"],"the door, I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"come"],"in to him, and will sup with him, and he with me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.21","order":"03.29.003.27321"},["b","21"],"To him that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"overcometh"],"will I grant to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"sit"],"with me in my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"throne"],", even as I also overcame, and am set down with my Father in his throne."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.22","order":"03.29.003.27322"},["b","22"],"He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1a","order":"03.29.003.27323"},["b","1a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 3:1 And unto the",["i","servant"],"of the church in Sardis, write; These things saith he",["i","who"],"hath the seven",["i","stars, which are"],"the seven",["i","servants of God;"],"I know thy …"],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1b","order":"03.29.003.27325"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.20"},"Rev. 1:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1c","order":"03.29.003.27327"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.4"},"Rev. 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1d","order":"03.29.003.27329"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.20.16,20"},"Rev. 1:20 (16, 20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1e","order":"03.29.003.27331"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.1f","order":"03.29.003.27333"},["b","1f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/2.1"},"Eph. 2:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.2a","order":"03.29.003.27335"},["b","2a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 3:2 Be watchful",["i","therefore,"],"and strengthen",["i","those who"],"remain,",["i","who"],"are ready to die …"],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.3a","order":"03.29.003.27337"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.23"},"D&C 39:23"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.3b","order":"03.29.003.27339"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.35"},"Luke 21:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.15"},"Rev. 16:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4a","order":"03.29.003.27341"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4b","order":"03.29.003.27343"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4c","order":"03.29.003.27345"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.11"},"Rev. 6:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.4d","order":"03.29.003.27347"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worthiness"},"TG Worthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5a","order":"03.29.003.27349"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.26"},"Rev. 2:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.60"},"D&C 76:60"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"TG Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5b","order":"03.29.003.27351"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5c","order":"03.29.003.27353"},["b","5c"],["span.small","GR"],"clothing."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5d","order":"03.29.003.27355"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-life"},"TG Book of Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"5e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5e","order":"03.29.003.27357"},["b","5e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/record-keeping"},"TG Record Keeping"],"."],["div",{"id":"5f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.5f","order":"03.29.003.27359"},["b","5f"],["span.small","GR"],"acknowledge, praise."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.7a","order":"03.29.003.27361"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sealing"},"Sealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.9a","order":"03.29.003.27363"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/49.23"},"Isa. 49:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.14"},"60:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"TG Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.10a","order":"03.29.003.27365"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/refuge"},"TG Refuge"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.10b","order":"03.29.003.27367"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temptation"},"TG Temptation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.11a","order":"03.29.003.27369"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testa